        "subject": "LU-13568 tests: Default lustre_revision: in test log yaml",
        "message": "LU-13568 tests: Default lustre_revision: in test log yaml\n\nWhen running tests on local clusters the default value\nlogged to yaml files for lustre_revision is empty.\n\nThis provides a default value from the running lustre filesystem\nvia the lustre sysfs version\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-8701\nSigned-off-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: Ic4c4f9285250ba8d5824bf3575700b14dc7607e5\n"
